Good luck!  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uveenublue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>veenublue</A> at: 3/20/02 11:17:02 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubloodshard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bloodshard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/20/02 11:17:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22895.topic&index=32>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://server3002.freeyellow.com/oggs/Bldshrdhead.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I think it's great except 1 problem</span><hr size=1> We were fighting last night &amp; after taking a death I went to look back to see what mob was hitting for before &amp; after defensive dropped &amp; the hits were gone.<br>
